<D>__{sir lawrence, what would you say to owning bluestar airlines with union concessions at $18 a share...and in the process hanging gordon gekko out in the wind to twist.... ?}
<A>__{sir lawrence leans back in his chair, equably...}
<C>__{wildman}
<D>__{i might be very interested, but why? why you mate how'd you get mixed up with gekko? he doesn't know the difference between raiding and insider trading. i do. the sec does. i hope you do...}
